      <p>Set up a formula for determining the number of respondents to the 1936 poll who said they voted in 1932 for either the Republican, Democratic, or Socialist or Other candidate. [Hint: Use columns D-G, L-O, and T-W.] What proportion of these voted for the Republican candidate?</p>
      <p>Sum: <var width="20"/> Proportion: <var width="20"/></p>
    </statement>
